OL,3,CMan in critical condition after being
OL,4,Cstabbed in Southport
OL,6,FA man is in a critical condition in
OL,7,Fhospital after being stabbed in
OL,9,FPolice were called just before 8pm on
OL,10,FFriday 29 March to Meols Cop Road,
OL,11,Fwhere the man, who's in his fifties,
OL,12,Fwas found with multiple slash wounds.
OL,14,FHe was taken to hospital after being
OL,15,Ftreated by paramedics.
OL,17,FMeols Cop Road was closed overnight
OL,18,Fand a police cordon was put in place
OL,19,Fwhile crime scene investigators
OL,20,Fcarried out forensic examinations at
OL,21,Fthe scene.
