OL,3,CMan in critical condition after being
OL,4,Cstabbed in Southport
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Gavin Mulcahy
OL,7,Fsaid: "An investigation is underway
OL,8,Fand is in the very early stages as we
OL,9,Fseek to establish what has happened on
OL,10,FMeols Cop Road.
OL,12,F"I would like to reassure residents
OL,13,Fthat at present we believe this was an
OL,14,Fisolated incident that took place
OL,15,Finside an address in the area.
OL,17,F"Our officers remain in the area and
OL,18,Fare committed to reducing knife crime
OL,19,Fin Merseyside and removing anyone who
OL,20,Fstores, carries and uses weapons on
OL,21,Four streets.
