OL,3,CMan in critical condition after being
OL,4,Cstabbed in Southport
OL,6,F"I would appeal to anyone who was on
OL,7,FMeols Cop Road this evening at around
OL,8,F8pm to please get in touch. You may
OL,9,Fhave seen or heard something
OL,10,Fsuspicious which has led to this
OL,11,Fviolent incident.
OL,13,F"I would also ask people who were in
OL,14,Fthe area to check their doorbell or
OL,15,FCCTV footage just in case they may
OL,16,Fhave captured something which may be
OL,17,Fvital to the case.
